<p>2.找到idea左下角Terminal窗口，输入：mvn idea:module<br><code>mvn idea:module</code><br><img src="https://img2020.cnblogs.com/blog/2282707/202101/2282707-20210117155820383-1474753529.png" alt="例图"></p>
